application\", \"main\": \"index.js\", \"scripts\": {\"test\": \"echo 'Error: no test specified' && exit 1\"}, \"author\": \"\", \"license\": \"ISC\"}"}, {"role": "user", "name": "QA", "content": "Successfully wrote to data/project_board/tickets/T-20231006-001-setup-structure.md"}, {"role": "user", "name": "QA", "content": "Transferred to ProjectManager, adopting the role of ProjectManager immediately."}, {"role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_R7HaSLJIW9GH593l7cB8KQaj", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "transfer_to_engineer"}, "type": "function"}], "content": "The ticket **T-20231006-001 - Setup Project Structure** has been completed and moved to **DONE** status. Here's a summary of the ticket's progression:\n\n- The project directories (`src`, `tests`) have been successfully created.\n- A basic `README.md` file has been written.\n- An initial `package.json` file has been generated.\n\nThe current state of the project structure looks good:\n- **Directories Created**: `src`, `tests`, and other components.\n- **README**: Basic information present.\n- **package.json**: Proper initialization.\n\nNext, I will continue the workflow by transferring the next ticket, **T-20231006-002 - JSON File Storage Implementation**, to the Engineer for execution. Let's proceed with that now."}, {"content": "Transferred to Engineer, adopting the role of Engineer immediately.", "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_R7HaSLJIW9GH593l7cB8KQaj"}, {"role": "user", "name": "Engineer", "content": "ID: T-20231006-002\nTitle: JSON File Storage Implementation\nStatus: TO DO\nOwner: Engineer\nDescription: Develop functionality to read from and write to a JSON file for storing Todo items.\nAcceptance Criteria:\n- JSON file is created and used to store Todo items.\n- Implement functions to read and write Todo items.\nTasks:\n- [ ] Create JSON file structure.\n- [ ] Implement read functionality.\n- [ ] Implement write functionality.\nLinks: N/A\nUpdates / History: Initial ticket creat